    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Microsoft Matter</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Michael N Bergelson letter on May 4 article lauds Microsoft's contribution to uniformity of personal computing</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Consumers and many computer companies have benefited from the Microsoft standard. The progress in personal computer technology was made because of the existence of such standards. Microsoft has made a much larger contribution to the uniformity of personal computing than I.B.M. did in the mainframe field.</p>
        <p>MICHAEL N. BERGELSON  Bronx</p>
      </block>
